{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"49778-feathered-friends","title":"Amis à plumes","description":"Les poussins manchots royaux partent en promenade et découvrent plein de manchots différents d'eux. Ils se font un ami et subissent une transformation radicale. Grandir est une sacrée aventure !","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Daniela  Hammond"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/49778-feathered-friends"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85544/size3/1bec959a236b14835f6f2e18865eb1e8.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85544/size6/1bec959a236b14835f6f2e18865eb1e8.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83470/size6/943775d7e9138347e7009e96d4dc707f.jpg","text":"Nous sommes des poussins manchots royaux.\nNous sommes inséparables.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83473/size6/53910547d484b55c238b8dcc0c2698ae.jpg","text":"Les manchots ne volent pas, ils nagent.\nMais nous, nous sommes trop petits pour nager. Alors, on marche.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83475/size6/c9ca6ff043910bb30cadc3ef4c6c4280.jpg","text":"Un jour, nous avons fait une grande promenade.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83476/size6/31b048d9993b830eb1fb3b27cb4d0776.jpg","text":"Nous avons marché pendant des heures,\njusqu'à ce qu'on tombe sur quelque chose\nque nous n'avions jamais vu.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83477/size6/918b5f43e4739ef58481fdabed711640.jpg","text":"— Oh, il a un drôle de truc\nsur la tête !","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83478/size6/dbd1ce02a55f0ffcd30aee36344fc3b2.jpg","text":"7/15","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83479/size6/530c288c9f277dad4b1f4e66d9316c81.jpg","text":"— Tu changes !","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83480/size6/576af22aa648f14c0bed5e2e5b09662b.jpg","text":"— Toi aussi !","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83481/size6/dfc430406301875afae446fc55acf7f7.jpg","text":"10/15","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83482/size6/edf7871d99973c6e41c2c7feb7787507.jpg","text":"— Pas mal !","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83483/size6/57948579a568bf741f38cdaed9ebca3f.jpg","text":"— Elle n'est pas si froide !","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83484/size6/ce54678a046f5b5826a8e89db69e157b.jpg","text":"— Mais qui va nous apprendre à nager ?\n— Moi, je veux bien.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83485/size6/e524184ebb795b9a3b4e1a07be47dfb2.jpg","text":"14/15","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83486/size6/7f4af1227124a5c968ec7f1c4c1954f6.jpg","text":"15/15","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":102}}